snippet.title: [Ancient Beast] Dread Knight vs Giani match 2
snippet.description:
Second recorded match of Ancient Beast.
Speeded up by about 240% to cut down thinking time.

This game is free open source and playable from the browser.
http://www.AncientBeast.com
